          %h2= docs_link 'User Guide', '/getting-started/'

          %p If you're new to Lita and want to learn how to use it, this is the place to start.

          %p Topics include a feature overview, installation, configuration, adding plugins, run time operation, and deployment.

        .col-md-6
          %h2= docs_link 'Plugin Authoring Guide', '/plugin-authoring/'

          %p If you're comfortable using Lita and you're ready to start developing your own plugins, refer to this guide.

          %p Topics include adapters, handlers, extensions, localization, testing, and publishing.
